<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <title>Dashboard SAS4ALL</title>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        }

        .box {
            border: 1px solid #00bfff;
            border-radius: 4px;
            padding: 20px;
            width: 60%;
            position: relative;
            margin: 40px auto;
        }

        .icon-circle {
            width: 40px;
            height: 40px;
            border: 2px solid #00bfff;
            border-radius: 50%;
            background-color: white;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            font-weight: bold;
            font-size: 18px;
            position: absolute;
            top: -25px;
            left: calc(50% - 20px);
        }

        .info-content {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 10px;
            color: #333;
        }

            .info-content .check {
                color: #d98fcd;
                font-size: 24px;
            }

        .saldo-box {
            border: 1px solid #00bfff;
            border-radius: 4px;
            padding: 30px 20px;
            width: 450px; /* largura fixa */
            position: relative;
            margin: 40px 260px 0 auto; /* alinha à direita com espaço */
            min-height: 130px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .euro-icon {
            width: 50px;
            height: 50px;
            border: 2px solid #00bfff;
            border-radius: 50%;
            background-color: white;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            font-size: 24px;
            position: absolute;
            top: -25px;
            left: calc(50% - 25px);
        }

        .saldo-link {
            color: #00bfff;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-size: 14px;
            position: absolute;
            right: 20px;
            top: 10px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <div class="box">
        <div class="icon-circle">i</div>
        <div class="info-content">
            <span class="check">✔</span>
            <span>Ementa sujeita a alterações por motivos imprevistos.</span>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="saldo-box">
        <div class="icon-circle">€</div>
        <a href="#" class="saldo-link" style="margin-top:25px">Saldo: X.XX€</a>
        <p style="margin-top:25px">Sem informação para apresentar</p>
    </div>

</body>
</html>
